Transform skewed data

-Price, Building Square foot, & Floor Area Ratio

-View new transformed price by categorical variables —We see there is variance in ranges when looking at the cat. variables and price which may mean they have an impact.

-View transformed price by numerics also —We see there is hopeful correlation between building square footage/Floor Area Ratio and price (but they may need to be looked at in the ransformed form)

Compp07_17$Trans_Price <- log(Compp07_17$Sale_Price)
Compp07_17$Trans_BldgSF <- log(Compp07_17$`Bldg SF`)
Compp07_17$Trans_FAR <- log(Compp07_17$`Floor Area Ratio`)
